# 7. ステージのセカイ

Minori: What happened? Where are we?
Minori: Is that a stage? There's another one over there, too.
Haruka: What's going on?
Shizuku: We were just on the rooftop, weren't we?
Airi: What is this place? It doesn't feel like a dream.
Minori: Oh, you're all here too! I was worried I was alone.
Minori: There sure are a lot of glow sticks. Is there a show about to start or something?
Miku: Yep! That's right, Minori!
Minori: Huh?! M-Miku?!
Rin: Miku! The show's about to start! Oh?!
Rin: You all finally came! We've been waiting for you, you know!
Minori: R-Rin's here too?! Oh my gosh! Am I actually shaking Rin's hand right now?!
Haruka: What in the world is going on?
Haruka: Miku and Rin are VIRTUAL SINGERS, aren't they? So how is it that we can talk to and touch them?
Miku: That's because we're in a world created by your combined feelings!
Shizuku: A world created by our feelings?
Miku: Yep! This SEKAI is created by the feelings you four have for idols!
Miku: We're here to help others discover their true feelings.
Rin: That's right! True feelings are transformed into new songs in this world♪
Rin: Though it looks like you haven't figured out what those true feelings are yet.
Haruka: .....
Minori: Feelings turn into songs? What exactly does that mean?
Rin: Explanations will have to wait until later! Right now, we just want you to enjoy our show♪
Miku: Yeah! We came up with this show just for you in the hopes it would cheer you all up! Please enjoy it!
Minori: Wait, does this mean we actually get to watch a real show with Miku and Rin?
Airi: Minori, come here a second.
Minori: Huh? Sure—ow ow OW!
Minori: Why did you pinch me?!
Airi: I just wanted to make sure this wasn't a dream.
Minori: Y-You could have pinched your own cheek, you know...
Shizuku: It looks like they're about to start.
Miku: Hi, everyone! Miku here!
Rin: And me, Rin♪ Thank you all for coming out to see us today!
Miku: We'll do our best to make sure you all enjoy the show! So without further ado, here's our first song!
Miku & Rin: ——♪ ——♪
Minori: Oh! She just winked at us!
Airi: How can you be having fun right now? We don't even know what's going on.
Miku: Sing along, everyone!
Minori: Everyone looks like they're having so much fun!
Minori: (The cute costumes, the atmosphere, the shining lights... I hope I can put on a show like this someday.)
Minori: (No, I definitely will! I'm going to become an idol for sure!)
Rin: Ready? Here we go!
Shizuku: They're perfectly in sync. They must really trust each other to be able to do that.
Haruka: You're right.
Airi: This is exactly the kind of show I always wanted to do.
Shizuku: Airi?
Miku: I'm sure you all know this next song!
Haruka: !!
Minori: Wow! Look at that! Everybody's glow sticks turned blue!
Minori: (It's the same as when Haruka did songs solo. Hehe. I remember waving my glow sticks like crazy that night.)
Minori: (Oh, but now that Haruka has quit, I guess that means I won't be able to see this again.)
Haruka: It reminds me of the ocean.
Minori: Huh?
Haruka: When you're on stage and everyone's glow sticks turn blue, it's like looking out at an ocean.
Haruka: All those happy, smiling faces bathed in a cool, blue light. It was so beautiful.
Haruka: I won't ever see it again, though...
Minori: Haruka...
Rin: Hurray! Another great success today♪
Miku: So what did you think of the show, everyone? Did it help cheer you up?
Minori: Yeah! It was great! I'm re-energized and ready to get back to work tomorrow!
Rin: Heh♪ I'm glad to hear that!
Minori: Why did everybody turn their glow sticks blue, though? I would've figured they'd be green for Miku or yellow for Rin.
Miku: Hehe. That's because your feelings take shape here in this world.
Minori: Feelings take shape?
Haruka: Miku. Rin.
Haruka: Thank you for letting us watch your show. It was wonderful.
Haruka: But could you send us home now, please?
Minori: Huh?
